    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch or chip, and the interior is in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, with a complete service history and all maintenance up to date. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in such impeccable state.",
