    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$3,800 - Calling all restoration fans and weekend mechanics! This car is the ultimate blank canvas and a fantastic project for anyone looking to dive into a full rebuild. While it's currently in rough shape and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it offers a great foundation for someone with the right skills and vision. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 3800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior is clean overall, though you will find some expected minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches that are typical for a car of this age. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, ensuring it is ready for the road without immediate major repairs. Inside, the cabin is tidy with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics function as intended. It represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a well-maintained vehicle at a fair price.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. It shows no signs of wear on the interior or exterior and is in perfect mechanical order. The car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and has a complete service history.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
